===Etymology 1===
From {{der|en|fr|apostrophe}}, or {{der|en|la|apostrophus}}, from {{der|en|grc|ἀπόστροφος|t=accent of elision}}, a noun use of an adjective from {{m|grc|ἀποστρέφω|t=I turn away}}, from {{mention|grc|ἀπό|t=away from}} + {{mention|grc|στρέφω|t=to turn}}.

